description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Gatinho purrs with a rating of 44, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 220, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 1 for East, Stringalong for South, and 1 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [220 Votes, Top 5% Score]
